		<descript>
			<langdata>eng</langdata>
			<langdata>chi</langdata>
			<abstract>Inner Mongolia Places, 1871 is a point theme representing towns &amp; mountains in Inner Mongolia in 1871 on the routes from the Dalai Nur Lake and Kalgan west to Jartai Lake and the route north to Ulaan Baatar;  digitized from H.M. Prezhavalsky "Map of East Asian Steppe"  1871-1873.  This dataset was developed by Irina Merzliakova (Inst of Geography) and Alexei Karimov (Inst for the History of Science), Russian Academy of Sciences.</abstract>
			<purpose>Projected for use with CHGIS Version 4.</purpose>
			<supplinf>English and Russian (codepage win1251)</supplinf>
		</descript>
